Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Defending freedom
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xbrj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Nov 1983
Anxiety after Grenada invasion as it becomes clear that US forces are now thinly stretched across the globe. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less